fields.bio: A bio refers to a brief description of a person's life, often shortened to "bio." It can be used as a synonym for biography or a biographical sketch.1 On Instagram, a bio is a description of an account that can be up to 150 characters long and sits at the top of the profile page, next to the profile picture. It is a snapshot of an account and a quick way to show users who you are and what you're about.
